title: GameMaker-Studio 1.1.1076 Auto-Update Experimental
description:
Ok, heres my latest release. This is the GMS 1.2 beta which includes YoYoCompiler and shaders. This is a new auto-updater that i made that now downloads updates directly from steam servers. The change allows me to get new versions out quickly and more stabley. Do note that this is a experimental version and that there may be bugs, please let me know in the comments of any bugs so i can fix them up before i release a stable build. 


-VeryC-
